-- Louis Dreyfus Considers Asset Sales as Alternative to IPO, Les Echos Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-23T05:07:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/louis-dreyfus-considers-asset-sales-as-alternative-to-ipo-les-echos-says.html
The family shareholders of Louis
Dreyfus are considering options including asset sales and an
initial public offering, French daily Les Echos reported, citing
an unidentified person.  The family may take up to a year to come to a decision, the
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  